.playwright-mcp
# The scripts directory holds inspect / dev / one-off tooling the image
# doesn't need — exclude it to keep the build context small. The exceptions are
# the bundled entrypoints: the builder stage runs `npx esbuild` over each to
# inline it into a self-contained `.cjs`, so those files (and their scripts-
# local imports) must reach the build context. Keep these negations in
# lockstep with the Dockerfile's esbuild steps. The cutover entries leave with
# the cutover scripts' post-migration deletion commit.
scripts
!scripts/migrate.ts
!scripts/migrate-firestore-to-pg.ts
!scripts/lib/blueprintFold.ts
!scripts/lib/firestoreRest.ts
!scripts/lib/format.ts
!scripts/lib/normalizeLegacyBlueprint.ts
